99-0458 (La. 4/1/99)

Nelson Nadine WILLIAMS v. JACKSON PARISH HOSPITAL, et al. No. 99-C-0458. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Jackson Parish Hospital; — Defendant(s); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Parish of Jackson 2nd Judicial District Court Div. “A” Number 26,-612, 26,391; to the Court of Appeal, Second Circuit, Number 31492-CA, 31551-CW, 31552-CW

Denied.

*559LEMMON, J. would grant the writ. KNOLL, J. not on panel.
